Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不行的吧  加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是接吻而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子  我想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要  你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:00:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回去路上当心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  小博  今天要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尝些甜点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是进行八朔节的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这几个选项吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花  别太粘着九澄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁喉技  锁喉技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  某个电视剧里说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱越是坎坷就越激烈来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能输  来场激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  还打算一起回去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来今天小要当班呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  作为图书委员工作比较忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是自己想要调查一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看起来挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学  还是先把这些放到桌上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好跟上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想调查的是嫦娥镇流传的民间传说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是都市传说那样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是现代版的怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排成队伍的红色萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜  在旧市街的小路上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人目击到发着红光的萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说看到的人就会遇上不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思议的是  这种萤火虫却没有被实际发现过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥镇流行种植八朔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔有八分切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说有撕得粉碎的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以八朔也是猎奇杀人的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  挺有趣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…就这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有点暧昧的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能有那种搞笑点的结局就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是相声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  小要对那些还真是着迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好将来拜小博父亲为师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不会了  以她的热情程度完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  星期一要好好做八朔节的练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要做那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  八朔节马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小博  下周见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的没那种兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你聊聊  学校的事什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太大声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  学校的事的话就叫上小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃会碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一诚前辈  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一小时  三十分钟也行  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他只是有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是太热了所以头有点昏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来就不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去倒些水来  稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了  真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  麻奈  你在生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说散步一个人也能行而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛  老爸说让我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明平时都不听话的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  难得一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好好享受景色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼…的雕像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼…和老爸说的嫦娥狼的传说有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了就告诉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定会咬住不放的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  那目光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在注视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说是不是发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪是没事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明突然就开始走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小提琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让心情平静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是白狼大人的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  真是很棒的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  不介意的话喝点茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请务必让我们品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你叫麻奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的姓一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫真那香织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}注：真那也读mana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果麻奈是我们家的孩子  就该叫真那麻奈了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位哥哥也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能合你口味太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不好意思  突然就受到这样的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  我平时都在招待邻居和路过的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个人生活  所以想要有人陪我说话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  香织姐姐  你平时都在拉小提琴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有时间的时候就拉  虽然技术不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我说不好  但我很感动的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈喜欢小提琴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然没有拉过  不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得  这音色真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拉拉看？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我不是太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个  我想会顺手的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我像麻奈你这么大的时候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就从姿势开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀放松
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用左肩和下巴下面支撑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当的有模有样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  哥哥你可不要随便乱说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就实际拉拉看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先从基本的基本开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  香织老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然叫我老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  老哥  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥的话出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是去「中心」拿胶囊去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你哥哥和你都是我家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  中心的储备已经很少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次能给你的量  这就是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  休息日叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因为我也有事要出来办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个  我一直在犹豫要不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢…前辈你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第一次见面时就喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道前辈你很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好几次我都想放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  可不可以请你下车？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定会回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在  你下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  打搅你这么长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么打搅  我很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈  下次再练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次你一定能拉出更美的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个漂亮的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉非常的高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓音如其人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你又说那种自以为很了解的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种温柔的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有香织小姐才拉得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不  只是有点迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  可以的话我来为您指路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  帽子忘记在香织姐姐那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我现在马上就去拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  已经不早了  明天再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  好啦  毕竟香织小姐也会在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来您是在做地质学的调查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您拿着地图  我还以为您是来观光的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我经常被人误会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是研究生院的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合您的口味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  这红茶很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是茶叶  泡的方式也很用心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在说这种无聊话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君  怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  妹妹把帽子给忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  研究期间有空请再过来坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会的话就来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织小姐的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是今天才遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我到底做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动静好像就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我全都知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的…萤火虫！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱他  他也爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明  只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢上他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是不会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不可能会明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上别人这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么而生下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  回答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了…维护戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  警察先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  来人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么打不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人  来人  来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说谎  请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的  的确是在这里  一个女人拿着巨大的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此狼神  尊五神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其伤悲  无人知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.06,0:23:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红月夜  唯狩猎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持大镰  震人心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.23,0:24:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么被隐瞒起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像整个小镇都在隐瞒这个秘密似的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那到底是什么  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  失控
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:34.19,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛しさはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:40.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみへと続いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:53.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君にもう一人きりで待たないでと　言い出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:59.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色あせてく　世界の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:06.03,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らは終りへ旅をする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:12.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その束の間に　君と出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:16.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命を削るように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:28.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の向こうに確かにあった　遥かな故郷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君とゆけるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:46.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜の向こうに　幻の空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:34.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:40.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接连着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:53.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口难开 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:59.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渐次斑驳  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:06.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至终焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:12.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之间  逢见君影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:16.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:28.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故乡迢迢  时之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无爱无心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:46.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻苍空
